description.text:
Adjust attached SCAD file to modify raspberry pi case height (by default - 23.4mm).
By default two mounts 15mm height are created.
Based on Hans Harder's Raspberry PI case with minor height modifications, but will fit to any raspberry pi case, just need to adjust the case height;

The World's Oldest Musical Instrument
I need this for a lecture I will be giving in<br />
A vulture-bone flute discovered in a European cave is likely the world's oldest recognizable musical instrument and pushes back humanity's musical roots.  The bone-flute pieces were found in 2008 at Hohle Fels, a Stone Age cave in southern Germany.  The newfound flutes, though, &quot;date to the very period of settlement in the region by modern humans ... about 40,000 years ago,&quot;
